=Description=

"[[Platoniq]]'s YOUCOOP is an online research platform born from the experiences with the Bank of Common Knowledge project (BCK). This platform gathers our research lines, texts about our methodologies and practical examples, such as games and significant projects created by other actors who are close to Platoniq's philosophy and practice. Basically, YOUCOOP contents want to spread alternatives able to apply the working methods of the Internet and P2P to several environments such as education, economics and social innovation."
(http://www.youcoop.org/en/)


